          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1012,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_019w7agEm3K7hiuVzGxzNkCf\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I've saved all your brainstorming answers. You're all set with a compelling foundation for your landing page! 🎉\\n\\nNow you have two options:\\n\\n**Option 1: Personalize Your Brand (Optional)**\\nAdd your logo, choose your brand colors, add social links, or upload custom images. Check out the Brand Personalization panel on the left. This takes just a few minutes if you have your assets ready.\\n\\n**Option 2: Build Right Away**\\nSkip personalization for now and hit \\\"Build My Site\\\" to see your landing page come to life. You can always customize the design later!\\n\\nWhat sounds good to you?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4819,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":145,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
