            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1213,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01TC4o2bDVTMNzZ3bTfwrq6R\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate that detail—the vetting process is important context. But I need to redirect slightly: **who is your primary customer?** Are you selling to podcast hosts, or to guests, or both?\\n\\nLet me be more specific:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"When you think about who's paying for Friend of the Pod, who are they? Podcast hosts looking for guests? Or are you monetizing both sides differently?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Podcast hosts (the ones actively searching for guests to book)\\\",\\n    \\\"Guests/experts (the ones looking for podcast appearances)\\\",\\n    \\\"Both—but we're leading with hosts as the primary revenue driver\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"This matters because it changes who we're writing the landing page for and what pain points we emphasize.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3005,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":193,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
