            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1088,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_017QqQvyRhfXpdmGqUhEwTk8\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great question! I want to reassure you:\\n\\n**Your data is safe.** Everything you've shared in this brainstorming session is:\\n- Used only to create *your* landing page\\n- Not stored, shared, or used to train any models\\n- Completely confidential\\n\\n**Your business idea is yours.** We're just helping you build a landing page to launch it. Think of us like a web builder—we're a tool to help you get your idea live, not a competitor or data collector.\\n\\nThe information you've provided stays between us and is only used to generate your custom landing page. Once your page is built, you own it completely.\\n\\nDoes that help ease your mind? Ready to build your landing page now?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4048,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":160,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
