            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_018HFjqWviaMceQvVYYk7Q1d\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate you wanting to move forward, but I need to understand your core business idea first—it's the foundation for everything else we'll build.\\n\\nLet me help you think through this. Here are some examples of what a strong business idea looks like:\\n\\n- **A subscription service for busy parents** that delivers pre-portioned, allergy-friendly meals so they don't have to spend hours meal planning\\n- **An AI-powered resume builder for career changers** that helps non-traditional candidates highlight transferable skills to land interviews at top companies\\n- **A done-for-you social media management service for local plumbers** that generates 3-5 qualified leads per month without them lifting a finger\\n\\nThe key is: **What does your business do, and what makes it different from what already exists?**\\n\\nHere's what I'm looking for:\\n- What problem are you solving or what need are you filling?\\n- Who are you solving it for?\\n- What's your unique angle or approach?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need to understand your core business idea first. What problem does your business solve, and what makes it different? Think about: what you're offering, who you're serving, and your unique angle.\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"A subscription service for busy parents delivering pre-portioned, allergy-friendly meals so they don't spend hours meal planning\\\",\\n    \\\"An AI-powered resume builder for career changers that highlights transferable skills to land interviews at top companies\\\",\\n    \\\"A done-for-you social media management service for local plumbers that generates 3-5 qualified leads per month\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What's your business idea?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2543,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":384,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
