        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1567,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1567,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_0155o7mU8CJRQrdsztqLuEqG\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great question! I want to reassure you:\\n\\n**Your data is completely safe.** Everything you've shared here is used solely to create *your* landing page. We don't use your business idea, data, or any information you've provided for any other purpose.\\n\\nHere's what happens:\\n- Your brainstorming answers are stored securely and only used to generate your custom landing page\\n- We don't train AI models on your data\\n- We don't share your information with third parties\\n- Once your page is built, you own it completely\\n\\nThink of this like working with a designer—you tell them about your business, they create your site, and that's it. Your idea and data remain yours.\\n\\nYou're in full control. If you have specific privacy concerns, I'm happy to address them!\\n\\nNow, you're all set to build your landing page. You have two options:\\n\\n1. **Personalize first** (optional): Upload your logo, choose brand colors, add social links, or upload custom images using the Brand Personalization panel on the left\\n2. **Build right away**: Click \\\"Build My Site\\\" to see your page with smart defaults—you can always customize later!\\n\\nWhat sounds good to you?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4153,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":266,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
