            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1458,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01KjeBXjWLXw6j7L4Ch9hpoT\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! 🎉 I've filled in the remaining sections based on your core messaging. You now have everything you need for a killer landing page.\\n\\nHere's what you have:\\n- **Your Idea:** Friend of the Pod solves the guest-sourcing problem at scale\\n- **Your Audience:** Podcast hosts (5K-500K listeners) who are drowning in the manual search process\\n- **Your Solution:** AI-powered matching that takes hours down to minutes\\n- **Social Proof:** Framework ready for your traction, metrics, and founder story\\n\\nNow you have two options:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Amazing! You're ready to build your landing page. Here's what you can do next:\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Personalize your brand (optional): Upload your logo, choose brand colors, add social links, or upload custom images in the Brand Personalization panel on the left\\\",\\n    \\\"Build right away: Skip personalization and hit 'Build My Site' to see your page live. You can always customize later!\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What sounds good to you?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":5209,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":263,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
