            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01P9CCHMji5kz4svyccJ1rG6\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great! I can see you've got some nice branding for **Launch10** with a rocket/launch theme. Before we dive into the landing page design, I need to understand your business idea better.\\n\\nLooking at your mockups, I can see the visual direction, but I need to hear from you directly: **What does Launch10 actually do? What problem does it solve, and what makes it different from other solutions out there?**\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Tell me about your SaaS tool. What does Launch10 do, and what makes it different from competitors?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Launch10 helps SaaS founders validate their product ideas before building—we've cut validation time from 3 months to 2 weeks\\\",\\n    \\\"Launch10 is an AI-powered email copywriting tool that generates personalized sequences for B2B sales teams—no templates, fully customized\\\",\\n    \\\"Launch10 is a project management tool built specifically for remote teams that struggle with async communication—it replaces 5 different tools\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Give me 2-3 sentences about what your tool does and what makes it stand out.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4424,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":277,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
