        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1759,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1759,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_014aGCtheLRegJVMfJwBTZCG\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great! I can see you've got a polished visual identity with that Launch10 logo. That's helpful context for the look and feel later.\\n\\nBut first—I still need to understand your audience better so we can write copy that really resonates with them.\\n\\n**Who are you primarily selling to?** Are you targeting:\\n- Established podcast hosts who already have an audience?\\n- New/emerging podcasters building their first show?\\n- Both equally?\\n\\nAnd **what's their biggest pain point?** Is it:\\n- Time spent searching for guests?\\n- Quality of guests they can access?\\n- Building credibility/getting on bigger shows (for guests)?\\n- Something else?\\n\\nGive me a clear picture of who you're solving for, and I'll move us forward.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Who is your primary customer—podcast hosts, guests, or both? And what's the main problem they're facing that Friend of the Pod solves?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Podcast hosts (established shows with 10k+ listeners) who spend hours vetting and reaching out to guests\\\",\\n    \\\"New podcasters who lack a network and struggle to find quality guests to launch their show\\\",\\n    \\\"Podcast guests who want exposure but don't know which shows to pitch to\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Be specific about who you're targeting and what pain point matters most to them.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3394,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":324,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
