            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01UwNuxWpthbGZogsxSnnrjQ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"It looks like I don't see any product photos in your uploads yet. No worries though! You have a couple of options:\\n\\n1. **Upload your product photos now** - Use the Brand Personalization panel on the left to upload images. You can add them to customize your hero section.\\n\\n2. **Build with smart defaults** - Click \\\"Build My Site\\\" and we'll create your landing page with professional placeholder imagery. You can always swap in your product photos later.\\n\\nWhich would you prefer?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4239,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":109,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
